<br>
So I got done killing Renux, and was going to hand in my parchment, only to find Anson was not up, there was a blue con (to 53) smuggler in his place. There isn't much I can do to solo blues anymore, so I asked around if people knew if the PH despawned or had any info on that front. Nobody knew, most said they never saw a PH so never had to bother.<br>
<br>
At 5am real time (I'm a night person), I gave the smuggler a rusty dagger to distinguish him, and logged off in front of him. Logged in at 9am, still had daggers. Noon, daggers. Logged in at 3pm, still had the daggers. By that point, I dusted off my level 60 mage and decided to kill the placeholder. Therefore, if it does ever despawn, it is over 10 hours real time.<br>
<br>
It still conned blue to level 60, so I was a bit hesitant to try soloing it (coulda been anywhere from 45-52), but I went ahead with it. There's 5 smugglers in that small area: Anson's PH flanked by one level 10 smuggler, and in another alcove is Cyra Sleawhisper (name?) or her ph flanked by two level 10 smugglers. At this time all 5 were smugglers, so I was able to slowly take out the blue ones. Note that some blue smugglers (2 I believe) path around the whole smuggler camp, and pass by the anson's enclosure, so I had to kill one of the roamers so I could pull the other ones into the main camp area without getting adds.<br>
<br>
Long story short. 16 minute spawn time, level 45 npc (estimate based on difficulty) that hit for double 117 and have at least 6k hp. They are <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> not</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> easy to solo as a 60 mage, in fact the last one killed my pet as I got off the killing nuke. I was lucky that Cyra was not up to start with, as she is a level 61 rogue trainer. Wouldn't want to pull her by mistake. If you go and Anson isn't up and Cyra <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> is</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> up, I would say you're out of luck because you'd need to pull smugglers past her and she would agro.<br>
<br>
Anson and Cyra spawned 16 minutes later and I got to log my rogue in and hand in my parchment to Stanos. Yay happy ending.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps,<br>
<br>
60 mage<br>
